show.description: On the eve of proposing to his girlfriend, Yun Chuqing, Ye Cheng becomes a vegetable due to an explosion. For ten years, Yun Chuqing cares for him without complaint, despite the pressure from her parents and others. Ten years later, Ye Cheng awakens and proposes to the Yun family, helping them become the most prestigious family in Wangcheng...
